skill_constraints: Single senior developer is a critical bottleneck, especially in Sprint 3.
resource_bottlenecks: Senior developer capacity for complex asynchronous tasks.
mitigation_strategies: Must rebalance workload across sprints; Senior dev must delegate.

skill_constraints: Relies on successful knowledge transfer from senior to mid-level.
resource_bottlenecks: Mid-level developer's ramp-up time on complex tasks.
mitigation_strategies: Shift tasks from Sprint 3 to Sprint 2 for mid-level dev. Implement pair programming on VCS-011-T1.
